{"tid":1579284,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"早兩日清塵唔記得插cpu 風扇，用左幾日怕唔怕有事","createTime":"2019-09-18T13:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T11:15:02.000Z","uid":46431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"18f8adca841ba5b7a46668d8fb9eebecb1022582","tid":1579284,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:38:19.000Z","msg":"早兩日拆左個intel cpu 風扇出黎掃塵<br />\n呢兩日玩game覺得lag左覺得怪怪地跟住睇下每粒core 都成90度<br />\n<br />\n即刻開個機箱望下原來無插cpu風扇個插頭<br />\n想問巴打熱左兩日會唔會有壞影響？<br />\n因為以前試過玩xbox360唔記得拎開遮住既野，部機熱過頭熄機，跟住無耐就壞左<br />\n<br />\nI5 8400 <br />\nMsi B360m pro vh<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dae98ba00f17ac2f5534f096433b70d8a874c60","tid":1579284,"uid":79793,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5afd10d054ef66f04961611b3209a884b9e10a","tid":1579284,"uid":294894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"開到機仲玩到者冇事啦"},{"pid":"6505133531b8751942e68785bb48062e070a89ce","tid":1579284,"uid":271516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:43:53.000Z","msg":"依家無事咪得，最多爆炸換過部"},{"pid":"7722f476f9ccbf83e2c2599cf5b10d7840bc1f34","tid":1579284,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ae5afd10d054ef66f04961611b3209a884b9e10a","tid":1579284,"uid":294894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"開到機仲玩到者冇事啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"成100度會唔會熱到塊底板有d位熔左？<br />\n<br />\n利申無咩電腦知識，thx"},{"pid":"816a0e3bb6c5ea6d3da4f852949338e158108a39","tid":1579284,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6505133531b8751942e68785bb48062e070a89ce","tid":1579284,"uid":271516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:43:53.000Z","msg":"依家無事咪得，最多爆炸換過部"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"